  <md:title>Potential, Kinetic, Free, and Activation Energy</md:title>
  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Define “energy”</item>
<item>Explain the difference between kinetic and potential energy</item>
<item>Discuss the concept of activation energy</item>
<item>Describe endergonic and exergonic reactions</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>8d36641e-73f4-4742-b869-a195f0399bc2</md:uuid>
